Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:05.26,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你很習慣那種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:10.62,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:12.49,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:16.61,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,被木嶋抓到把柄了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.97,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.89,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:28.61,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼做也不會湧現靈感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:30.23,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,截稿日也不會延期的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.35,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,矢部先生還在等著原稿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:33.75,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:36.60,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青 不用擔心我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.90,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是矢部先生 你都等那麼多天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:43.99,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,每當老師被自己家的瀑布擊打之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:46.68,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定會誕生一部大傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:48.36,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大傑作？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:52.98,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:00:59.26,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,等著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.13,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,矢部先生 你完全沒喝下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:03.17,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,快去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:06.16,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師還沒有休息我不能去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:09.00,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,作為編輯就該和作家共渡難關
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:12.79,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,父親會因為害死了編輯而變成殺人犯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.36,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣連載也會中斷的 你快去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:19.40,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你稍微陪我一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:27.00,aochan-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\blur4\c&HE8AC11&\pos(523.2,928.667)}木嶋{\r\blur4}君{\blur4\c&HE8AC11&}等{\r\blur4}不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.39,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,烤肉慶典的會場在這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:31.36,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,牛豬雞羊熊鹿什麼肉都有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:33.66,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還有舞台活動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.13,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:37.41,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,奶子祭典？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:40.15,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師之前說過對這裡有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:41.09,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我來取材
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:42.66,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,奶子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:44.34,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,酒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:46.00,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,肉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:47.91,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,肉慾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:52.15,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,歡喜雀躍 放聲高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.20,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是酒池肉林嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:57.76,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此 肉慾總會與性慾相連
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.37,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師也是著眼於此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:02.69,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,肉慾即性慾？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.28,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.21,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡很危險 別離開我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:08.87,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.99,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被肉慾的旋渦絆住雙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.09,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青一個人肯定頂不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.54,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬間就會被捲進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:26.11,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡充斥著現充的味道 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.31,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來我還沒吃午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.90,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,矢部先生你要吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.35,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:45.51,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕啊 肚子好餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.02,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:51.23,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:53.38,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明看起來很不適應這種場合的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:54.76,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.29,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,比剛才的小姐姐們要可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.46,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看哪裡 別提胸部的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:03.80,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.25,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別想撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.62,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.96,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雅才是為什麼穿著這身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.27,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,還用說嗎 我在打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.65,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在缺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:18.52,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別用那種憐憫的視線看我 你個大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.81,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.29,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我打工是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.04,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:25.80,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,能麻煩你確認一下庫存嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:27.45,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:30.95,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是堀江嗎 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.99,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他剛剛是不是喊了雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.48,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是一起來打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:39.28,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能在下次休息的時候一起出去玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:42.18,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人？為了兩個人出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.51,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種酒林肉池的地方一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:51.00,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青 要倒下的時候 可以來依靠我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.60,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥的小哥哥 是誰啊 是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:00.82,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是爸爸的擔當編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.14,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:03.59,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我擔當的作品有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:06.92,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,「狂亂哭泣」「床上金句100條」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.53,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這書名難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.85,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 這會讓木嶋知道爸爸是做什麼工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:15.11,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:20.29,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是青父親的大學後輩 名叫矢部宗一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:23.58,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.35,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,作為一個父親的後輩來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:31.53,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你和堀江…和女兒的關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.84,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道你關係好的基準
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.84,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但你作為一個同級生來說關係也挺好的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:41.08,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我和堀江關係也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:46.14,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來我們可以叫關係好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.99,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經拜訪了上百次青的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:53.31,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的存在一次都沒有成為話題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:55.67,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:59.51,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,拓海 再不回去工作要被罵了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.26,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩位好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.72,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.38,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,經典的現充情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.41,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無疑問他們整天卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.25,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們兩個沒在交往啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.41,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都直呼其名了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.11,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,直呼其名是通向做愛的第一步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:21.74,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這裡還有肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.31,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人一起烤肉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:27.50,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就已經是愛欲發展到什麼程度都不奇怪的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.50,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,牛背肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.07,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…上好的牛背肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:32.53,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,矢…矢部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:33.57,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.60,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還是繼續取材吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:36.95,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:44.42,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 木嶋君 糊了糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.87,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 高岡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.85,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,拓海 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.07,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟高岡先生有點可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.70,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 都怪我在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.20,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,拓海好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:02.31,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,難得和店長同姓才好不容易讓他叫我名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.14,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,休息的時候去哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.68,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,薪水也有不少 真是期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:11.07,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易才和拓海一起打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.80,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的矢部先生真是大帥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.95,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還直呼青的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.86,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一年八個月零九天 18次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.82,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,三個月二十天 32次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:31.76,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,12天 108次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:36.28,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然喜歡牛背肉的情侶屬於熱戀中的那種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.48,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡牛舌的意外地熱情度也很高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.22,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那熱情度低的是喜歡炸豬排的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.80,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人應該沒在交往…才對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:46.08,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.66,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,木嶋應該是喜歡我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:53.45,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想和喜歡的人做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:57.66,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是說他們沒在交往的話關係也太好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.00,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是現充的距離嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.55,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.06,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.12,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也太近了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.55,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:04.70,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我討厭自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.97,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想別人直呼我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:14.81,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.36,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.81,aochan-sceen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(975.8,907)\fad(700,0)}直到兩人直呼其名為止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:26.67,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 果然根本就不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:30.40,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全就變成那種無趣的青春電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.10,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種名字我才不想被叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.60,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,叫什麼名字啊 假惺惺的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.13,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.46,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.56,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,木嶋君 你為什麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.66,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是休息時間 我就在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.37,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他聽到我叫他名字了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.62,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒和矢部先生在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.14,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,無視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.70,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然這對現充來說不算什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:05.34,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是又走散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.16,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人真帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:14.10,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候就認識他了 也就沒啥感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.72,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他經常去你家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:18.45,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他很崇拜我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.10,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也經常照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.66,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,崇拜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.34,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟你關係好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:28.85,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好吧 我高中的時候也請他當了家教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.91,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:32.52,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是三者面談的老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.88,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他聰明到你去請教他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.64,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是東大畢業的 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:42.35,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,東大…那是能教你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.15,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青 找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.57,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:51.76,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,木嶋君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:55.15,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青 過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:56.61,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.56,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別去 青
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:03.91,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.71,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,青 要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:11.61,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有話要和她說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.29,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,等下我肯定會回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:22.56,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,0次 真年輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:31.99,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.24,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,終於冷靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:45.09,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是果然 我腦子裡全是堀江的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.01,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,腦子完全被轉暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:49.77,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是我的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:50.82,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.69,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因為我沒得到你的回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:55.03,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經等不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.51,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓你迷上我
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:06.58,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好性感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:07.88,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:07.63,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:08.86,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,內衣就穿這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.86,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那裡碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:10.88,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:13.01,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,小青在海裡也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:14.48,aochan-text,NTP,0,0,0,,奶子好大
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,aochan-text,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:29.56,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,わかんないこと多すぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:32.69,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,「わかろうとしてる時点ナンセンス」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.74,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,君の言葉、難しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:38.95,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,君の魅力もワンダーランド
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:44.87,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,チャイムが鳴ったら逢いにゆくね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.04,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,夢中にさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.29,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}A i a i a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:54.13,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,100から始まる  カウント
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:59.30,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,君に近づけるリミット (Ah Ah Ah)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:03.01,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,じつに単純明快なココロ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:06.02,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,0に近い打率で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:11.56,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,青春のうちに射抜けるか！？ （Ah Ah Ah）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:15.07,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,じつに難しい僕らの関係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:18.53,aochan-opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,WONDER WONDER WONDERFUL WONDER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:29.56,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白的事情太多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:32.69,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,「嘗試去了解時就已經顯得愚昧」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.74,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的話語 難以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:38.95,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的魅力就是仙境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:44.87,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,當鐘聲響起時  就想要去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.04,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我沉迷在你的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:54.13,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,從一百開始的倒計時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:59.30,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,與你接近的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:03.01,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,實在是單純明快的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:06.02,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是精確度接近於零的命中率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:11.56,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,也能在青春中命中你嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:15.07,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的關係非常複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:18.53,aochan-opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,奇妙 奇妙 絕妙的奇蹟
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:16.23,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}頭の中いっぱいに溢れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:21.95,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}君のことで占拠率１２０％
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:26.45,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}純粋無垢なこの気持ぎゅっと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:31.42,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}投げつけたり　伝えたい全部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:37.46,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}恋だって気づく前から
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:43.55,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}君に全部ごと惹かれていたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:49.10,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}そうとも知らずに　そうやってまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:56.82,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}無邪気な笑顔見せるから困ったもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.24,aochan-edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fsp-8}気づかないかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:16.23,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}你在我的腦中充溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:21.95,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}120%占據了我的腦海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:26.45,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}這份純粹無垢的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:31.42,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}想要全部傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:37.46,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}在發現這份戀情之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:43.55,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}就已經被你深深吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:49.10,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}在不知不覺中我依舊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:56.82,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}以天真無邪的笑容面對你 是否感到困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.24,aochan-edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}能否發現我的心意？
